# Proxy Configuration Examples for Docker2 Bot Detection

# ============================================
# OPTION 1: No Proxy (Default - Current Setup)
# ============================================
# Leave PROXY_URL empty or commented out

# ============================================
# OPTION 2: Single HTTP Proxy
# ============================================
# PROXY_URL=http://username:password@proxy.example.com:8080
# PROXY_TYPE=http

# ============================================
# OPTION 3: Single SOCKS5 Proxy
# ============================================
# PROXY_URL=socks5://proxy.example.com:1080
# PROXY_TYPE=socks5

# ============================================
# OPTION 4: ScraperAPI (RECOMMENDED - FREE & PAID)
# ============================================
# FREE: 1,000 requests/month - Sign up: https://www.scraperapi.com/signup
# PAID: Starting at $29/month for more requests
SCRAPER_API_KEY=your_free_api_key_here
SCRAPER_RENDER_JS=false
SCRAPER_COUNTRY_CODE=US

# ============================================
# OPTION 5: Other Paid Proxy Services
# ============================================

# Bright Data ($168+/month)
# PROXY_URL=http://lum-customer-xxxxxxxxx-zone-residential:password@zproxy.lum-superproxy.io:22225
# PROXY_TYPE=http

# Smartproxy ($39/month)
# PROXY_URL=http://user:password@gate.smartproxy.com:7000
# PROXY_TYPE=http

# Oxylabs ($75+/month)
# PROXY_URL=http://customer-country-country_code:password@pr.oxylabs.io:7777
# PROXY_TYPE=http

# ============================================
# OPTION 5: Proxy Rotation (Multiple Proxies)
# ============================================
# PROXY_ROTATION_ENABLED=true
# PROXY_LIST_FILE=/app/proxies.txt
# Place proxy list in proxies.txt, one per line:
# http://proxy1.com:8080
# http://proxy2.com:8080
# socks5://proxy3.com:1080

# ============================================
# NOTES
# ============================================
# 1. **ScraperAPI is EASIEST:** Just set SCRAPER_API_KEY, no proxy setup needed
# 2. Free tier (1,000/month) is great for development and testing
# 3. Proxy credentials should be in environment variables, not committed
# 4. Use strong passwords for proxy accounts
# 5. Residential proxies (Bright Data, Smartproxy) are better for Cloudflare
# 6. Avoid free proxies - they're unreliable and often malicious
# 7. Test proxy with: curl -x http://proxy:port https://httpbin.org/ip
# 8. ScraperAPI usage example: https://www.scraperapi.com/documentation
